MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2008-0311. Dennie v. Hurst Constr., Inc.

Lorain App. No. 06CA009055, 2007-0hio-7038. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
